articles.title: First nitrogen gas execution in US has happened, but did it go as expected? - ABC News
articles.description: Kenneth Smith, 58, became the first American to be executed by nitrogen gas.
articles.content: The Alabama attorney general said Friday that nitrogen gas is now a "proven" method of execution and that he believes more such executions will follow after the first one in the U.S. was carried out.… [+3776 chars]
